title: 030tango Short – Saludos2018 – San Francisco #Saludos18
description:
Join us on the trip from Berlin to San Francisco to record Clarisa Aragon and Jonathan Saavedra for the Saludos2018 clip!

Music by Tangopianissimo
https://www.tangopianissimo.com

If you love Tango videos, support 030tango on
https://www.patreon.com/030tango

Recorded during
Nora's Tango Week 2018
http://tangoweek.com

Visit 030tango for more videos
http://www.030tango.com

Recorded in June and July 2018
#030tango #tango  #Saludos18
